WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.860 --> 00:00:06.839
Hi, I’m Ken Burns.

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:11.800
To tell the stories in my films I rely on
a rich diversity of voices.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:15.440
Won’t you take a moment to listen to voices
of a different kind.

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:18.090
They come from the natural world.

00:00:18.090 --> 00:00:22.100
They may even surprise you.

